/F1 10.00 Tf 54.00 533.55 Td (ts_rank_cd is a PostgreSQL full-text-search ranking function. It scores how well a tsvector) Tj
/F1 10.00 Tf 54.00 520.05 Td (matches a tsquery.) Tj
/F1 10.00 Tf 54.00 500.55 Td (The cd means cover density. It rewards results where the query terms appear close together and) Tj
/F1 10.00 Tf 54.00 487.05 Td (are concentrated in a small section of text.) Tj
