/F1 10.00 Tf 54.00 433.05 Td (score into a more convenient range. It mainly affects the score shape, not the basic relevance) Tj
/F1 10.00 Tf 54.00 419.55 Td (idea.) Tj
/F1 10.00 Tf 54.00 400.05 Td (Example: if the query is "hybrid search ranking", a chunk containing "Hybrid search ranking is) Tj
/F1 10.00 Tf 54.00 386.55 Td (done with reciprocal rank fusion" should score better than a chunk where hybrid, search, and) Tj
/F1 10.00 Tf 54.00 373.05 Td (ranking are scattered far apart.) Tj
